+introText: Between a patient and a clinician. Between a measurement and a decision. Between a promising idea and something that can work safely in the real world.
+focus:
+  - title: Primary health
+    text: Practical tools that fit the pace, constraints and relationships of everyday care.
+    tag: Point of care
+    mark: +
+  - title: Monitoring
