+    tag: Human systems
+    mark: ↗
+featureKicker: Healthcare / direction 01
+featureTitle: Make the signal easier to trust.
+featureText: A concept space for products that turn complex physiological information into something useful at the point where care decisions happen.
+featureStatus: Research / shaping
+featureCode: PFT—HC—01
+featureList:
+  - clinically useful, not merely novel
+  - designed around real workflows
+  - clear about risk, limits and next steps
+principlesTitle: Start with the person. Design for the system.
+principles:
+  - title: Useful first
+    text: A feature only matters if it helps someone do something better.
+  - title: Trust is designed
+    text: Explain the signal, the uncertainty and the responsibility around it.
+  - title: Care is connected
+    text: Products succeed when the surrounding service is considered too.
